\v 12 TheseВҰ155001 are the people who ruin yourВҰ155015 loveВҰ155013 feastsВҰ155013 when they eat without shame and only look after themselvesВҰ155023. They're like cloudsВҰ155025 that are blown away by the wind without bringing the needed rain or treesВҰ155034 that don't produce any fruit then are doubly useless by falling over;
