\v 24-25 Our master, Yeshua the messiah, is the infallibleВҰ155274 one who is quite capable of looking after all of us so that we can standВҰ155279 blamelessВҰ155287 in frontВҰ155280 of him and praise him in his full honour and greatness. Let us honour and praise our only God and saviour, acknowledging his greatness and power and authority through Yeshua from before the creation, right through these current times, and in the age to come. May it be so.
